    "content": "<p>Write the solution of the following LPP</p>\n<p>Maximize $$Z=x+y$$</p>\n<p>Subject to $$3x+4y\\le12,x\\ge0,y\\ge0$$.</p>\n<p>Which point the value of Z is maximum?</p>",
